Commit: Save the new , updated Cumulative Factors, and block.timestamp to DataStore.7
4.3 Position-Level O(1) Calculation
This global architecture allows for O(1) complexity for individual position updates. When a user opens a position, the protocol records a "snapshot" of the global cumulative factor at that moment.
Position Structure (Position.Props):
sizeInUsd: The size of the position.
fundingFeeAmountPerSize: A snapshot of the global cumulativeFundingFactor at the last interaction.9
